<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    
    <h1>About me</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "Oregon.JPG", height: 300,  alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img'%>   
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
                    <h4><%=skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
               class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
               role="progressbar"
               aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
               aria-valuemax="100"
               style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
               >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
      

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I come from a diverse background, a "Zac" of all trades you might say.  I've always been passionate about technology, and when I found software development I was hooked! The ability to create something out of nothing and take a vision and make it a reality is so fulfilling!
        </p>

        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="jobHistory"
        >
            Job History
        </button>
        </p>
                <p>
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="education"
        >
            Education
        </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
            <h5>Freelance Developer - Bottega 2017</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
            <h5>Operations Specialist - Entrata 2016</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
            <h5>Clinic Lead Over Patient Services - St. Lukes 2012 - 2015</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

          <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
            <h5>Boise State University</h5>
            <h6>Bachelors of Science - Health Science </h6>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
            <h5>National Academy of Sports Medicine</h5>
            <h6>Personal Fitness Training Certification</h6>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
     </div> 
  </div>
</div>



